summary: 该插件用于检测致远OA A6系统中setextno.jsp文件的SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定payload验证是否存在漏洞并返回相关信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect SQL injection vulnerabilities in the setextno.jsp file of ZYSoft OA A6 system. It verifies the existence of vulnerabilities by sending a specific payload and returns relevant information.
